headline.main: LONDON EXPECTS MOVE IN BLACK SEA; Germans Are Believed to Be Concentrating Craft and Supplies at Axis Ports

lead_paragraph: LONNDON, April 1 -- There is little doubt that the Germans are concentrating small landing craft and supplies in the Black Sea ports of Varna and Constanta, it was said here today.
abstract: London expects German Black Sea moves as Axis masses troops and craft, that area
